PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the THUNDERCHILD FIRST NATION BAND surrenders, for an indefinite term, all of its rights and interests in and to the oil and gas that may exist within, upon or under specified portions of 14 of their reserves in Saskatchewan, for the purpose of allowing the Crown to issue leases, etc., to third parties for oil and gas exploration and development.
